entry.def: When things such as blood vessels or the pupils of your eyes dilate or when something dilates them, they become wider or bigger.

example.ex: At night, the pupils dilate to allow in more light...
example.tran: 到了晚上，瞳孔就会扩大以接收更多光线。

example.ex: Exercise dilates blood vessels on the surface of the brain.
example.tran: 运动会使大脑表层的血管扩张。

means.word_mean: 1. made wider or larger in all dimensions;
